### Google Places API Text Search example
### Replace YOUR_API_KEY with a valid key.
POST https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places:searchText
Content-Type: application/json
X-Goog-Api-Key: YOUR_API_KEY
X-Goog-FieldMask: places.id,places.displayName,places.formattedAddress,places.location,places.rating,places.userRatingCount,places.businessStatus,places.primaryType,places.googleMapsUri

{
  "textQuery": "kebab Depok Sleman"
}
